WEBVTT

00:01.040 --> 00:03.560
WOMAN: Last season
on A Place To Call Home...

00:06.040 --> 00:07.520
I love you with all my heart.

00:08.600 --> 00:09.760
Marry me.

00:10.760 --> 00:12.480
Yes.

00:12.480 --> 00:15.400
We're in love, Papa.
We're going to get married.

00:15.400 --> 00:18.680
I'm suggesting you let them
live together for three months

00:18.680 --> 00:20.480
as if they were married...
No. Impossible.

00:20.480 --> 00:22.680
..in every way except sharing a bed.

00:22.680 --> 00:25.520
Anna could move into your home
in a separate room

00:25.520 --> 00:27.520
and live the life of Gino's wife.

00:27.520 --> 00:29.800
While Anna lives with the Polettis

00:29.800 --> 00:33.000
testing her resolve
to marry inappropriately,

00:33.000 --> 00:35.920
you will spend three months
at Ash Park doing the same.

00:37.080 --> 00:39.480
Mother will do anything
to sabotage you.

00:39.480 --> 00:40.520
Let her.

00:40.520 --> 00:42.480
She's tough.
I'm tougher.

00:42.480 --> 00:46.600
I caught a glimpse last night
into the true nature of Sarah Adams.

00:46.600 --> 00:48.640
I saw a very dangerous woman.

00:48.640 --> 00:50.960
I don't care what it costs.

00:50.960 --> 00:54.280
Find something
that will rid us of her forever.

00:55.320 --> 00:59.240
The child I had, my darling,
it was you.

01:00.520 --> 01:03.960
Our situation is a complication
you don't need in the mix.

01:03.960 --> 01:06.400
I understand if you don't tell
the family just yet.

01:06.400 --> 01:08.520
I've come to talk
about our daughter.

01:12.520 --> 01:13.880
JAMES: I want you to cure me.

01:13.880 --> 01:16.240
MAN: I will need
your total commitment.

01:16.240 --> 01:17.240
You have it.

01:17.240 --> 01:19.880
OLIVIA: What if Dr Stewart
can't cure him?

01:19.880 --> 01:22.960
He just said that...
What if he can't?

01:22.960 --> 01:26.440
I'll still love him. Will you?

01:26.440 --> 01:27.880
What's it worth to you

01:27.880 --> 01:30.880
for the world not to find out
that your son's a queer?

01:33.080 --> 01:36.680
He's been seen with Harry Polson.
We're being blackmailed.

01:36.680 --> 01:38.320
You cross me on this...

01:39.520 --> 01:40.720
..you'll regret it.

